Package: weatherAlerts
Type: Package
Title: Get Active Weather Alerts from the United States National Weather Service
Version: 0.1
Imports: RCurl, XML
Suggests: weatherAlertAreas
Date: 2016-03-10
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Cook", , "ianmcook@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Retrieve information about current United States National Weather
  Service (NWS) watches, warnings, and advisories, via the Common Alerting
  Protocol (CAP) and Atom Syndication Format (ATOM). Alerts are currently
  limited to the 50 United States and the District of Columbia.
URL: https://github.com/ianmcook/weatherAlerts
BugReports: https://github.com/ianmcook/weatherAlerts/issues
NeedsCompilation: no
License: MIT + file LICENSE
